<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410017.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "46.217mm" ver = "01" gw = "167" gh = "114"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Attach bleeder plug cap.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
After completing bleeding operation, apply fluid pressure to brake lines and check for leakage.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Replenish new fluid into reservoir up to specified level. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A4106001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check brake pedal stroke the stroke is so large, repeat entire procedure of bleeding.
</ptxt>
</s1>
